          <p><i>How long would it take to place a phone call to Pluto?</i></p>
          <p>Due to its elliptical orbit, light (and therefore a telephone call) can take up to 5.5 hours in each direction from Earth to Pluto.</p>
          <p><i>Hope Pluto doesn't put you on hold!</i></p>
        </div>
